Package: qwanadate
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative Wood Anatomy dating
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Samuel", "Bouchut", , "Samuel.Bouchut@uqat.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Samuel Bouchut <Samuel.Bouchut@uqat.ca>
Description: Shiny application to interactively date tree-rings in QWA images.
    qwanadate is an interactive app designed to help absolute dating of wood 
    anatomical images analysed with the qwanamiz Python package.
